\subsection{Costs}

\subsubsection{A thief must spend (250 + 150 \x Rank) Silver Pennies
per year to maintain a proper set of thieving equipment.}

A thief who does not spend the above amount operates as if he were two
Ranks less proficient when performing any of the abilities described
in \ref{thief:picklocks}, \ref{thief:removetraps} and
\ref{thief:pickpockets}. If his Rank for these abilities is
temporarily reduced to a negative number, he may not perform them
until he meets expenses.

The above cost does not include any trap containers (see the Basic
Goods Cost List) that the thief may wish to purchase.
